headline: Camden Property Trust Announces Participation in Citi’s 2026 Global Property CEO Conference and Provides First Quarter 2026 Operating Update
summary: HOUSTON, February 27, 2026--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today that the Company will participate in Citi’s 2026 Global Property CEO Conference. Camden’s roundtable discussion has been scheduled for Tuesday, March 3, 2026, at 1:30 PM Eastern Time. The event will be webcast live in a listen-only mode at camdenliving.com in the Investors section, and an audio archive will be available on the Company’s website shortly after the event concludes.
